title: LibriVox's Short Story Collection 005
description: LibriVox's Short Story Collection 005: a collection of 20 short essays and fiction in the public domain read by a variety of LibriVox members. For further information, including links to online text, reader information, RSS feeds, CD cover or other formats (if available), please go to the LibriVox catalog page for this recording. For more free audiobooks, or to become a volunteer reader, please visit librivox.org. Download M4B (200MB)
subject: librivox; literature; audiobook; short stories
source: Librivox recording of a public-domain text

reviews.reviewbody: I haven't listened to the whole collection, but I wanted to say that this version of "Rikki Tikki Tavi" was my first introduction to the classic story and I liked it a lot. The American-sounding male reader, Mark Butler, puts a lot of expression into the animal characters.
